OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FMPs voted earlier this year to force
OL,7,Fthe disclosure of documents relating
OL,8,Fto his time as ambassador.
OL,10,FThe more than 1,000 pages of documents
OL,11,Fin the second tranche released on
OL,12,FMonday included records of WhatsApp
OL,13,Fexchanges between Lord Mandelson and
OL,14,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,15,FMcFadden that revealed the latter's
OL,16,Ffrustration with his colleagues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FIn May 2025, in the wake of local
OL,7,Felection setbacks and the Runcorn by-
OL,8,Felection defeat, Mr McFadden said:
OL,9,F"Lot of manoeuvring here this week.
OL,10,FAngela (Rayner), Gordon (Brown).
OL,11,FDoesn't feel good for Keir."
OL,13,FHe also complained that Labour MPs
OL,14,Fwere "asking the wrong questions".
OL,16,F"Every meeting I have is 'who can we
OL,17,Ftax in order to pay benefits to
OL,18,Fothers'," he said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@\O]vD@FOUvD@aO]xD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FMr McFadden, who was the senior
OL,7,Fminister in the Cabinet Office at the
OL,8,Ftime, also acknowledged Sir Keir's
OL,9,Fauthority risked being destroyed by a
OL,10,FLabour revolt over welfare reforms.
OL,12,FIn June, shortly before the Government
OL,13,Fcaved in to provide a series of
OL,14,Fconcessions to rebel MPs, he said: "I
OL,15,Fthink it's very bad. Defeat, pull Bill
OL,16,For gut it all destroys his authority."
OL,18,FMr McFadden became the Work and
OL,19,FPensions Secretary, responsible for
OL,20,Fthe welfare system, in September 2025.
OL,26,@vD@dOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
