OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FLord Mandelson was highly critical of
OL,7,FSir Keir's operation in messages,
OL,8,Fsaying the Prime Minister "lacks
OL,9,Fverve" and that Chancellor Rachel
OL,10,FReeves could not explain where
OL,11,Feconomic growth would come from.
OL,13,FIn a message to Mr McFadden in July
OL,14,F2025, he said: "I went into No10 after
OL,15,FI saw you. It is beleaguered and
OL,16,Fbereft. It requires complete revamp
OL,17,Fand infusion of purpose and confidence
OL,18,Fto get anywhere."
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@FO]vD@POUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
