CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FIn the same month, he said the
OL,7,FGovernment "doesn't do policy,
OL,8,Fgenerally speaking, well enough", in a
OL,9,Fmessage to pensions minister Torsten
OL,10,FBell.
OL,12,FMr Bell told him: "That is definitely
OL,13,Ftrue ` everyone seems to think it's
OL,14,Fsomeone else's job to get the policy
OL,15,Fright... Which is very odd."
OL,17,FLord Mandelson replied: "As the saying
OL,18,Fgoes, rubbish in rubbish out..."
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@`O]tD@SOUwD@\O]yD@YOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
