OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,FMPs will have the opportunity to
OL,7,Fdebate the second tranche of files on
OL,8,FWednesday.
OL,10,FAlso in the files:
OL,12,F` Lord Mandelson was disparaging about
OL,13,FWes Streeting's "hysterical" comments
OL,14,Fafter the former health secretary
OL,15,Fmessaged him about recognising a
OL,16,FPalestinian state.
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
