OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,F` Lord Mandelson "declined to comply"
OL,7,Fwith a request to hand over his
OL,8,Fpersonal phone to allow access to his
OL,9,FWhatsApp messages and other
OL,10,Finformation related to his appointment.
OL,12,F` Cabinet Office officials initially
OL,13,Fbelieved he would not require
OL,14,Fdeveloped vetting because of his
OL,15,Fstatus as a member of the House of
OL,16,FLords, but later decided he would.
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
