OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780369437
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,F` Emails showed that the Foreign
OL,7,FOffice gave Lord Mandelson access to
OL,8,F"higher classification material" on a
OL,9,Fcase-by-case basis before his
OL,10,Fdeveloped vetting was cleared.
OL,12,F` Lord Mandelson sent a note to then-
OL,13,Fforeign secretary David Lammy about
OL,14,Fbeing potentially made ambassador,
OL,15,Fsaying "if you were minded to appoint
OL,16,Fme I would make sure you never regret
OL,17,Fit".
OL,19,F` Lord Mandelson lobbied several
OL,20,Fministers to support his bid to become
OL,21,Fchancellor of Oxford University.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@`O]wD@HOUyD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
