OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after
OL,4,CMandelson files lay bare splits
OL,6,F` He requested to be put on the
OL,7,FForeign Office payroll after a
OL,8,FShanghai conference took place as he
OL,9,Fhad committed to a paid speaking
OL,10,Fengagement that he would attend
OL,11,Fvirtually on behalf of his company
OL,12,FGlobal Counsel. However it is not
OL,13,Fclear whether he actually went ahead
OL,14,Fand spoke at the conference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
